<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Event Cancellation Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #8e44ad;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Event Cancellation Notification</h2>
    <p>Hello <%= attendeeName %>,</p>
    <p>We regret to inform you that the event "<%= eventName %>" scheduled for <%= eventStartDate %> has been canceled.</p>
    <p>Please contact us for further details or if you have any questions.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>Agenda Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
